blog.name: livylove151
blog.title: Imagines ❤️
blog.description: I write imagines for the Outsiders, any YouTubers. Requests are OPEN!

summary: David Dobrik’s Sister (Grayson Dolan x Reader)
title: David Dobrik’s Sister (Grayson Dolan x Reader)
body:
Request: hi! can u make an imagine where the reader is David Dobrik’s sister and she’s dating Grayson Dolan? thank u so much!

Your POV 

Being David Dobrik’s little sister you were used to being around other youtubers and being hit on by him and his friends. But when it came to Grayson Dolan, David had no idea you were friends with him. It all started when you became friends with Emma Chamberlain, you two being the same age and all it kind of helped. Not that anything was wrong with Liza, Kristen, Natalie or Carly and Erin, they were just older than you and sometimes you had nothing in common with any of them.

When Emma started to be in a few vlogs you guys instantly became good friends. You two started to hang out more, go to small coffee shops, hang out at her place and you were glad to finally have someone your age to hang out with besides your idiot brother and his guy friends who sometimes hit on you. 

David was also very protective when it came to you. Never allowed Todd or Dom to hit on you and for that you were grateful but he also never really appreciated you hanging out with the guys either. But he never told you that you couldn’t just gave you a lot of shit for it. 

So when Emma introduced to the Dolan twins you never told David about it. You were too afraid he was going to say no. But they were really sweet and really funny and you couldn’t resist. The one that you immediately clicked with was Grayson. You knew that Ethan and Grayson were twins but they were totally different.

Grayson and you started to text more, hang out a lot more, when it was just the two of you- you noticed he started to flirt with you. And you’ve never really had a boyfriend before. Not that you’ve never had dates because you’ve had you just weren’t used to guys paying attention to you.

Grayson then asked you out one day and you immediately said yes. And from then on you guys have been together. For almost four months. And David still had no idea. 

He noticed you seemed to be happier and that you were texting more and leaving the house more but he never really asked any questions. So you figured you didn’t have to tell him if he never asked. 

Grayson, on the other-hand, wanted to tell everybody. And you felt bad for telling him to hang on a little longer. You were over at his place laying on his bed scrolling through instagram, Grayson’s head on your lap. 

“I just don’t understand why we can’t tell everybody,” Grayson whined as he pulled your phone away from you. 

“We’ve been over this. I don’t want David to know yet because I don’t know how he will handle things,” You said running a hand through his hair. 

“I’ve met David before, (Y/N), he’s a chill laid back guy I don’t think he will mind,” Grayson said sitting up. You sighed. 

“Maybe he wouldn’t mind that we are together but he may mind me keeping it a secret for four months,” You explained. Grayson leaned over and kissed your cheek several times. 

“i want to let everybody know that you’re my girlfriend and that I love you,” He said wrapping his arms around you. You looked over at him and studied his eyes. He looked so understanding and caring. 

“Fine, we can tell him. But I’m not responsible for any prank or dumb crap my brother decides to do,” You said putting your hands up in surrender. Grayson smiled and pulled you in for a tight hug, making sure to get a lot of kisses in as well. 

**********

It was the next day you decided to invite Grayson over. David was on the couch editing a video. You walked over to him and sat down. His eyes never left the laptop’s screen. 

“Hey brother,” You said slowly as you gently nudged him in the side. He glanced over at you. 

“You sound like you broke something. What did you do?” He asked shutting his laptop. 

“I didn’t do anything. I’m just letting you know that I’m having someone come over that’s very important to me and I want you to behave so no pranks,” You warned. He scrunched his eyebrows in confusion. 

“Okay? But you never have people over besides Emma,” he said. You shrugged as you heard the doorbell ring. You stood up and walked to the door. David followed you.

When you opened the door there stood Grayson. His hands in his jogger pockets smiling at you and your brother. David looked down at you with a weird look on his face. 

“Why is Grayson Dolan here?” David asked. Grayson walked in and stood right beside you and arm snaking around your waist. 

“Um, well Grayson is my boyfriend. And we’ve been together for about four months now. And I know I should’ve told you but I didn’t know if you were going to freakout or yell at me,” You explained as you looked at David’s face. He looked between the two of you not saying a word. 

“So you’ve had a boyfriend for four months and didn’t tell me?” you nodded and waited for the yelling to begin. 

“David, I want you to know that I love your sister and I’m not going to hurt her or anything like that,” Grayson said stepping towards him. David was silent for another minute but burst out laughing. 

“Oh my gosh my sister is dating one of the Dolan twins. This is going to be perfect clickbait. And don’t worry I’m not going to be all protective and all that stupid shit. But if you do hurt her I will kick your ass,” David said pointing at Grayson. Grayson laughed. 

“So you’re okay with all this?” You asked. 

“Of course I am. I’m just confused on how YOU scored with one of the Dolan twins,” David said giving you a little push. You rolled your eyes and flipped him off. You turned back to your boyfriend and smiled. 

“Told you he’d be okay with it,” Grayson said giving you a small smile. You wrapped your arms around his neck. 

“I guess you were right,” You said as he leaned down and put his lips on yours. 

“EWWWW, none of that!” David yelled causing you and Grayson to pull away from each other and laugh.

“We’ve been over this. I don’t want David to know yet because I don’t know how he will handle things,” You said running a hand through his hair. 

“I’ve met David before, (Y/N), he’s a chill laid back guy I don’t think he will mind,” Grayson said sitting up. You sighed. 

“Maybe he wouldn’t mind that we are together but he may mind me keeping it a secret for four months,” You explained. Grayson leaned over and kissed your cheek several times. 

“i want to let everybody know that you’re my girlfriend and that I love you,” He said wrapping his arms around you. You looked over at him and studied his eyes. He looked so understanding and caring. 

“Fine, we can tell him. But I’m not responsible for any prank or dumb crap my brother decides to do,” You said putting your hands up in surrender. Grayson smiled and pulled you in for a tight hug, making sure to get a lot of kisses in as well. 

**********

It was the next day you decided to invite Grayson over. David was on the couch editing a video. You walked over to him and sat down. His eyes never left the laptop’s screen. 

“Hey brother,” You said slowly as you gently nudged him in the side. He glanced over at you. 

“You sound like you broke something. What did you do?” He asked shutting his laptop. 

“I didn’t do anything. I’m just letting you know that I’m having someone come over that’s very important to me and I want you to behave so no pranks,” You warned. He scrunched his eyebrows in confusion. 

“Okay? But you never have people over besides Emma,” he said. You shrugged as you heard the doorbell ring. You stood up and walked to the door. David followed you.

When you opened the door there stood Grayson. His hands in his jogger pockets smiling at you and your brother. David looked down at you with a weird look on his face. 

“Why is Grayson Dolan here?” David asked. Grayson walked in and stood right beside you and arm snaking around your waist. 

“Um, well Grayson is my boyfriend. And we’ve been together for about four months now. And I know I should’ve told you but I didn’t know if you were going to freakout or yell at me,” You explained as you looked at David’s face. He looked between the two of you not saying a word. 

“So you’ve had a boyfriend for four months and didn’t tell me?” you nodded and waited for the yelling to begin. 

“David, I want you to know that I love your sister and I’m not going to hurt her or anything like that,” Grayson said stepping towards him. David was silent for another minute but burst out laughing. 

“Oh my gosh my sister is dating one of the Dolan twins. This is going to be perfect clickbait. And don’t worry I’m not going to be all protective and all that stupid shit. But if you do hurt her I will kick your ass,” David said pointing at Grayson. Grayson laughed. 

“So you’re okay with all this?” You asked. 

“Of course I am. I’m just confused on how YOU scored with one of the Dolan twins,” David said giving you a little push. You rolled your eyes and flipped him off. You turned back to your boyfriend and smiled. 

“Told you he’d be okay with it,” Grayson said giving you a small smile. You wrapped your arms around his neck. 

“I guess you were right,” You said as he leaned down and put his lips on yours. 

“EWWWW, none of that!” David yelled causing you and Grayson to pull away from each other and laugh.

title: My favourite YouTubers
body:
As a middle school student I loved all your typical youtubers: Zoe, Bethany, Alfie, Connor etc. That’s what really got me into watching and loving YouTube. In high school I moved on from all the beauty and life vloggers and loved BookTube for the longest time. Now in university I still watch YouTube, but for much different reasons than I used to. Now I try to watch people that help me “adult”, get my life together and just better myself as a person. I thought I could share some of my favourites. 

For school
Jack Edwards - I love Jack cause he just motivates me to do work and study. It always helps to romanticize studying when you lose motivation. Watching other people study can really help.
https://www.youtube.com/user/thejackexperience

Eve Cornwell - Eve is so funny and super relatable, and I just love watching how motivated she is. But she also shows you how you don’t need to be the best or the smartest to succeed in life and I love that.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCM8qRGoiaLwmMv31L7xeeEQ

John Fish - John is so inspirational for being a good student. He has his shit together and is ready to get down to business. He’s a Canadian going to Harvard, which is another thing that I find super cool. 
https://www.youtube.com/user/MrFish235

Thomas Frank - I don’t watch all of Tom’s videos, but he has some pretty good tips on school and studying.
https://www.youtube.com/user/electrickeye91

Lifestyle
Nika Erculj - I love Nika cause she is in the process of getting her shit together. She’s had loads of struggles in the past, but is super honest and open about her health and that is really refreshing to see.
https://www.youtube.com/user/NikasInnerBeauty

Elena Taber - Elena is probably my favourite YouTuber. I discovered her while she still lived in California. I just love her perspective on life, her style and everything about the way she lives her life. 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDBroOWVP4aN8SYM0br6sJQ

Matt D’Avella - A funny, low-key minimalist. Enough said.
https://www.youtube.com/user/blackboxfilmcompany

Really fucking funny (cause everyone needs a break every now and again)
Cody Ko - Definitely the funniest YouTuber right now in my opinion. Just watch him. Do it! 
https://www.youtube.com/user/codyko69

Noel Miller - Cody’s counterpart; equally funny, comedic genius. 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCuTQDPUE12sy7g1xf1LAdTA

Danny Gonzalez - I love Danny. He makes my day any time I watch him.
https://www.youtube.com/user/ActualDannyGonzalez

Drew Gooden - Danny’s counterpart. Drew has a bit more diversity in his videos, which I find quite refreshing.
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCTSRIY3GLFYIpkR2QwyeklA
